{
  "stem": "6719.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she went to see a friend, and this friend sent her to another friend, and to another friend.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And every second night, or third night, she was shoveled from one place to another.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She washed the dishes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She took care of the kids.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she washed the diapers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she cleaned the home, and all that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But she was hidden during that whole time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Vienna, until the Russians came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, because she's well endowed-- in other words, she has, uh, size, whatever it is, Omar the Tentmaker.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I love her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She's a beautiful woman.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She uh-- and the Russians liked big busted women, and they raped everything in sight, so she just fled and went to Salzburg, and that's where I was stationed.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was in the American Army, the CIC.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's where I met her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I fell in love.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, that's where I was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I-- I chased them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I found them and--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--had no mercy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Um, yeah, very briefly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, she talked things that she feels were very stupid things that she has done.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, here is a woman that has no paper, and she's, what, 19 years old?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And 18 years old?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And 20 years old?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she went to dances in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, that takes a lot of guts, or stupidity.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, I--I-- I call it-- She'd call it-- she said, Dennis, I didn't realize, I didn't care, blah, blah, blah.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I never thought there would be any danger.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Only once was she in danger, she told me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She went on the street car, and there was somebody that lived in the house where she grew up, and she thought that-- or she's almost sure that he recognized her.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
